underlying_goal: To scrape sandbagging prompts from a list of AI safety research papers.
friction_detail: Three sub-agents responsible for scraping papers got stuck and were unresponsive for over 12 minutes, requiring them to be killed and restarted.
primary_success: Successfully orchestrating 8 parallel sub-agents to scrape and synthesize a comprehensive compendium of sandbagging prompts from multiple research papers, including handling agent failures and restarts.
brief_summary: The user tasked Claude with scraping sandbagging prompts from a literature review. Claude orchestrated 8 parallel sub-agents to process the papers, handling several stuck agents by restarting them. The task was successfully completed, resulting in a compiled document of prompts from all sources.
